  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They killed them over there with the same way, with the [? injection. ?] At the same night, after they took the men from there, they brought to us all the women and the children that were with us.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they killed them right in the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we burned them over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the end of the gypsies, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, at that time, they kill them with the-- with the gas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those children-- of course, we didn't see them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And never we saw them, because we were never in contact with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the 100 people remaining from the crematorias-- they needed us to-- to burn some other dead people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At the end, they put us to make some holes from the crematorias, like I show you in the picture of my brother over there, that you don't see nothing, because they blew up the crematorium over there.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why you cannot see nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they brought some other people from Auschwitz to help us in a rush, to do some [INAUDIBLE] on the cements, on the walls, and so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew it, that they want to put some dyna-- dynama-- dynamite to blow up the crematoriums, which it took three, four days, or five days, to do all those holes.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they told us, if you make so many holes-- because we were two guys making a hole, one holding the-- that kind of tool to make the hole, the other one with a heavy hammer hitting on top.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you make two, three holes, or four holes, or five holes a day, then you can rest-- which everybody want to do the holes faster, just do not work anymore.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
